pan style=&quot;font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;** By purchasing one of our handmade products you are entering into the agreement that the product you receive may vary slightly from the one pictured on our website. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;All care is taken with orders but please be aware that as this product is made from timber, the grain and colour may vary with each one made.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Bamboo Birth Announcement Discs', 'Bamboo Birth Announcement Discs', 'Bamboo Birth Announcement Discs', 'Bamboo-Milestone-birth-announcement -Discs-gift');
